<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa; 
            color: #343a40; 
            padding-top: 160px; /* Space for the fixed header */
        }

        header {
            background-color: #007bff; 
            color: white;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            padding: 20px 0;
            height: 100px;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #0056b3; 
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: orange;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: large;
        }

        .nav-link:hover {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .card {
            border-radius: 1rem; /* Rounded corners */
        }

        .card-body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6f42c1 0%, #d63384 100%); /* Gradient background */
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-success {
            background-color: #28a745; /* Green button */
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-success:hover {
            background-color: #218838; /* Darker green on hover */
        }

        h1, .lead {
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Text shadow for depth */
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .card-body {
                text-align: center; /* Center text on smaller screens */
            }
        }
    </style>
    <title>Home Page</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="py-3 text-center">
        <h4>Welcome to MoseH Telemed Application</h4>
        <nav>
            <ul class="nav justify-content-center">
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" href="/">Home</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Patient Login</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Patient Registration</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/doctors_login">Doctors Login</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="card shadow">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h1 class="display-4 text-primary">Welcome, Patients and Doctors!</h1>
                <p class="lead">This site is to help patients who cannot access health care services for them to meet our Doctors.</p>
                <hr class="my-4">
                <p>We offer various telemedicine services to connect you with healthcare professionals.</p>
                <a class="btn btn-success btn-lg" href="/about" role="button">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="mt-5">
            <h2 class="text-center">Our Services</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Virtual Consultations</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Connect with doctors from the comfort of your home through video consultations.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Prescription Services</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Get prescriptions sent directly to your pharmacy after a consultation.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Health Monitoring</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Monitor your health with our remote monitoring services and regular check-ins.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-5">
            <h2 class="text-center">Benefits of Telemedicine</h2>
            <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item">Convenient access to healthcare professionals.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Reduced travel time and costs.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Increased flexibility in scheduling appointments.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Improved health outcomes through timely consultations.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-5">
            <h2 class="text-center">Testimonials</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="card-text">"Telemedicine has changed my life! I can consult my doctor without leaving my house." - Sarah K.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="card-text">"I love the convenience of being able to get my prescriptions online." - John D.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="card-text">"The doctors are very attentive and I feel like I'm getting great care!" - Emily R.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
